# Round 01 experiment log

## Environment

```bash
cd research-artifacts/novel-inversion-vs-shard
python3 -m venv .venv
.venv/bin/pip install torch numpy scipy matplotlib torchvision
```

## Command

```bash
.venv/bin/python code/benchmark_round01.py 2>&1 | tee logs/experiment_round01.log
```

## Config (from benchmark)

- MNIST: N=12, resize=14 (d=196)
- SurrogateQFL: dim_g=160, seed=7
- SHARD L3: n_batch=120, adam_steps=800, L-BFGS max_iter=300
- LAPIN: 5 lstsq seeds + 48 random, 25 GN steps each, L-BFGS polish

## Key stdout (metrics JSON)

```
SHARD L3:  MSE=0.0127  PSNR=19.0 dB  snap_match=0.58  runtime=4.9s
LAPIN:     MSE=0.0877  PSNR=10.6 dB  snap_match=0.00  runtime=4.1s
```

